  <summary date="2020-03-31T16:20:18Z" status="Introduced in Senate">GI Education Benefits Fairness Act of 2019

This bill expands eligibility for receipt of GI education benefits as a dependent under the Post-9/11 Educational Assistance Program. Specifically, the bill includes certain unmarried persons as dependents who can receive a transferred entitlement to educational assistance.</summary>
